"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"üê• gm hatchlings!\\n\\nToday we will be covering how to buy and sell NFTs on [OpenSea](https://opensea.io/), a decentralized marketplace to trade NFTs (non fungible tokens) and digital assets!\\n\\n**First, be sure to checkout these prerequisite guides**\\n\\n* [How to set up MetaMask](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/-UWjheu5bsRvMUa78_O242czkl5AwHs58jT9S-p-0u0)\\n* [What is an NFT?](https://ethereum.org/en/nft/) (by Ethereum)\\n\\nOnce your crypto wallet is set up and you know a bit about what NFTs are, let us learn a little more about OpenSea!\\n\\n### üêü What is OpenSea?\\n\\nOpenSea is a decentralized NFT marketplace where you can post, buy and sell digital assets! OpenSea is a the largest NFT platform boasting over 80 million NFTs and conducting over $10 billion (USD) in trading volume üò≥\\n\\n> Check out this video by OpenSea to learn more!\\n\\n[https://youtu.be/gfGuPd1CELo](https://youtu.be/gfGuPd1CELo)\\n\\n## üê≥ How can I buy an NFT on OpenSea?\\n\\n1. Visit [Opensea.io](https://opensea.io/)\\n2. Click the wallet icon to the top right, and connect your wallet to the site\\n3. When buying an NFT on OpenSea, you‚Äôll see one of three options:\\n   1. **Buy Now** - The seller listed a fixed price and you can buy it immediately by paying the listed price\\n   2. **Make Offer -** Owner hasn‚Äôt posted it up for sale, but make an offer and they can accept/decline it\\n   3. **Place Bid -** The seller is accepting bids until a certain date (auction) and the highest bidder gets the NFT\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/0lk4pyhD3AMOEkO6nlin1.png?height=260&width=1776&&size=medium)\\n\\n1. ***Note:*** *To place a bid or make an offer you need wETH (wrapped Ether), a cross-platform token that represents ETH‚Äôs value exactly 1:1*\\n   1. *You can wrap your ETH for wETH directly on OpenSea*\\n   2. *Once you‚Äôve wrapped some wETH, you can place bids as many times as you want completely free!*\\n   3. To learn more about wETH, visit their website [here](https://weth.io/)\\n\\n![Wrapping ETH for wETH on OpenSea](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/txBfQNocQSxUkyxf5wUoU.png?height=938&width=1678)\\n\\n1. Visit a collection and select an NFT you‚Äôd like to own (we‚Äôll be looking at [Crypto Coven](https://opensea.io/collection/cryptocoven)!)\\n   1. ***Note:*** *Floor price refers to the lowest price of an NFT in the collection (aka the minimum price of the collection)*\\n2. Click **Buy now** or **place bid** to purchase or bid depending on the NFT you want!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1jjUfvQzPFA5nw_39XIpt.png?height=486&width=1598&&size=medium)\\n\\n1. Click **Confirm checkout** and wait for a confirmation message!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9mZmAGnSksQsw2NUU1AGN.png?height=830&width=1322)\\n\\n**üñº That‚Äôs it!! You have officially bought your first NFT!**\\n\\nYou should be able to view it by clicking on your profile in the top right corner on OpenSea!\\n\\n![Click this icon to edit your profile & view your NFTs!](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/VhD1zyp5xqZ02QCneZiNc.png?height=216&width=862)\\n\\n## üìå How do I Sell NFTs on OpenSea?\\n\\nNow that you own some NFTs, it‚Äôs time to look at how you would sell them on OpenSea!\\n\\n1. Go to your **Profile** by clicking the person icon to the left of the wallet icon\\n2. Click the NFT you would like to sell\\n3. Click **Sell** to open the Listing Menu\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/HcVHRIiAFTMdrwe1avq4b.png?height=738&width=1362)\\n\\n1. As a seller, you have two options:\\n   1. **Fixed Price -** Set a fixed price for any number of days\\n   2. **Timed Auction -** Set an auction for a number of days where the highest bidder wins\\n2. Let‚Äôs sell our NFT at a fixed price\\n3. Enter the price you would like to sell at and click **Complete listing**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ht5fMrdlWKka0ZGFfnkTk.png?height=878&width=780)\\n\\n***Note:*** *To finalize your sale, you will have to do a few things first with your wallet first*\\n\\n1. **Initialize your wallet -** You will need to do this **only** if it‚Äôs your first time selling on OpenSea\\n2. **Approve this item for sale -** You will need to approve every item for sale, but once you do, re-listing the item is free (only a signature request will be needed)\\n3. **Confirm listing** - Confirm the signature request to finalize your posting\\n\\nOnce you get your confirmation message, that‚Äôs it!\\n\\n**ü•≥ You‚Äôve officially posted you first NFT for sale!** \\n\\nWe hope this guide was helpful and easy-to-follow!\\n\\nBe sure to checkout our Mirror and follow us on Twitter for all things web3!\\n\\n[https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/rabbithole_gg](https://twitter.com/rabbithole_gg)\\n\\nüíï Stay curious frens!\",\"timestamp\":1640186101,\"title\":\"Tutorial: How to Buy & Sell NFTs on OpenSea\",\"publication\":\"rabbithole\"},\"digest\":\"a_lQk3Wznu76C7bDKLU7F3xeO5g6B3h-8hzaGxkX0Tg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x75A548a2Df9Ba12af496BD5364F642C9cE3C3976\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eKUlBLd_oUFUSo7a9O6fO-UcefvbvTKIDodn6cfer3E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"OXIaur0YsjtTsE6aX9W2kCpYF0tL6AqPK7mbmTHqupQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"MmDiMg98xc1XyTYg2W01kPDgiu4I9w5FyrTWi_cZ0sBD5I27KPNFXtFcmHGOCAmHkwwB713Jo4IUX_L4wQos9w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x51271ff6c4d655f8e32f3306b478fe7d375dd8408b0163dd06467a952d2a93307b2bf840465eb502cc572261c0f72b74ac9ba166418b61a0ca1909a81fb8655f1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eKUlBLd_oUFUSo7a9O6fO-UcefvbvTKIDodn6cfer3E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"